data.text: El Tiempo was a newspaper self-defined as a National Magazine Ilustrated that was published in Masaya. Its Director was Anselmo Gutiérrez. It contained poetry and short pieces of literature. Extent: One issue of 24 pages. Publisher(s): Anselmo Gutiérrez P. Volume and issue number: NA / NA.
